<add-different-days>
When the New Day button is clicked, please bring up a nice 
calendar/date picker UI.  This date picker default to the current
day, but also allow the user to pick any previous day.

When a day is picked, the app should check to see if the day already
exists with tasks, and if it does, display an error and do nothing.
If the picked date does NOT have any tasks, then make that the currently
selected date in the left side date list, show the currently selected date
in the edit pane in the normal way, with a blank Task line to start.

The rest of the application behaviour should remain exactly the same.
</add-different-days>

<show-hour-totals>
